Product Description:
DETAILS OF INFINIX SMART 7 4GB RAM 64GB ROM.Infinix is near to launch Smart 7 series of smartphones and it has been suggested that the devices may be launched in the upcoming months of this year, based on recent leaks.Then let's move on to the latest features of the Infinix Smart 7.Topping the list of features is a dual-lens camera setup, a 6.6-inch full-HD+ display, and a massive 6000 mAh battery with fast charging.In light of the fact that the smartphone might be launched with a massive 6000mAh battery pack, it is likely that users of this phone will be able to use it all day long on a single charge.Furthermore this Infinix Smart 7's a powerful Helio A22 SoC chipset with a couple of Octa-core CPUs.A dedicated memory card slot will enable users to expand the cell phone's memory up to 256GB in addition to the smartphone's 64GB of internal storage.
There is no doubt that the Infinix Smart 7 is very attractive due to its dual camera setup along with its attractive design.The phone's primary camera sensor is 13 MP, while the second is a 0.3 MP macro sensor.There is a single 5MP camera with an LED flashlight located on the front of the device.The brand new Infinix Smart's 7 is packed with a bigger 6.6 Inches TFT LCD display that can easily support the HD resolution of 720 x 1612 Pixels beside them it offers 500 nits of extra brightness.The improved display of the Infinix Smart's 7 allows for richer and more vibrant colours, greater clarity and better visibility in direct sunlight, making it an ideal device for watching movies, playing games, and browsing the web.The improved brightness also ensures that users will be able to use the device more comfortably in direct sunlight and other bright environments.
